headline: Duke Energy proposes milestone new natural gas plant to help build a stronger energy future for South Carolina
summary: Duke Energy announced today the company's intent to submit an application to the Public Service Commission of South Carolina (PSCSC) for approval to build a new natural gas power plant in Anderson County.
